WEBVTT

00:00:13.119 --> 00:00:13.919
That hurts!

00:00:14.480 --> 00:00:15.240
Are you okay?

00:00:16.839 --> 00:00:17.359
Xiaobao.

00:00:17.679 --> 00:00:18.320
Are you alright?

00:00:19.039 --> 00:00:20.519
You little Jinx!

00:00:20.640 --> 00:00:21.760
Are you blind?

00:00:22.039 --> 00:00:23.160
If you make your brother cry again,

00:00:23.440 --> 00:00:24.519
I'll break your legs!

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:25.920
I think you did it on purpose.

00:00:26.239 --> 00:00:27.160
If something's bothering you, say it.

00:00:30.440 --> 00:00:31.160
Hurry up and cook dinner.

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:33.000
I've been busy selling vegetables,

00:00:33.439 --> 00:00:34.479
I haven't had time to cook.

00:00:34.759 --> 00:00:35.320
Then go do it now!

00:00:35.840 --> 00:00:36.520
What are you standing around for?

00:00:36.719 --> 00:00:38.039
You always favor my brother.

00:00:39.960 --> 00:00:40.679
We feed you,

00:00:40.880 --> 00:00:41.719
we clothe you,

00:00:41.840 --> 00:00:42.840
we raised you all these years,

00:00:43.119 --> 00:00:44.520
and you're still not satisfied?

00:00:44.960 --> 00:00:46.000
Are you trying to start a rebellion?

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:46.920
So much fun, so much fun!

00:00:55.560 --> 00:00:57.679
Regarding your husband's accident claim,

00:00:58.039 --> 00:00:59.159
the documents you submitted

00:00:59.159 --> 00:01:00.560
I'll enter them into the system today.

00:01:01.679 --> 00:01:03.119
It'll take three to five business days.

00:01:03.119 --> 00:01:03.520
Alright.

00:01:04.079 --> 00:01:04.799
Got it.

00:01:05.040 --> 00:01:06.359
Anyway, once the payout comes through,

00:01:06.359 --> 00:01:07.439
notify me right away.

00:01:07.439 --> 00:01:08.239
The sooner, the better.

00:01:08.959 --> 00:01:09.439
Okay.

00:01:09.680 --> 00:01:10.840
I'll contact you once there's an update.

00:01:10.840 --> 00:01:11.280
Good.

00:01:16.640 --> 00:01:17.280
Xu Lingling.

00:01:19.560 --> 00:01:21.000
There are new developments in the case.

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:22.359
We need you to cooperate with us.

00:01:29.799 --> 00:01:31.560
A guest's life was put in danger,

00:01:32.079 --> 00:01:34.359
and the resort had no emergency response.

00:01:34.640 --> 00:01:36.640
It's fair to demand compensation, right?

00:01:36.879 --> 00:01:37.799
Honestly,

00:01:37.799 --> 00:01:39.879
I don't really want this money.

00:01:40.159 --> 00:01:41.760
It makes me look so petty.

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:43.120
But my husband...

00:01:43.280 --> 00:01:43.879
If he hadn't

00:01:43.879 --> 00:01:45.879
insisted on supporting his old flame,

00:01:46.599 --> 00:01:48.040
he wouldn't have had a heart attack.

00:01:49.799 --> 00:01:50.599
What about the insurance?

00:01:51.280 --> 00:01:52.400
My husband and I

00:01:52.400 --> 00:01:54.120
always had a habit of buying insurance.

00:01:54.480 --> 00:01:55.599
I have a policy too.

00:01:55.920 --> 00:01:57.040
Since something happened to him,

00:01:57.519 --> 00:01:59.280
and police issued a death certificate,

00:01:59.719 --> 00:02:00.959
my claim for the payout

00:02:00.959 --> 00:02:02.040
is perfectly reasonable, right?

00:02:02.680 --> 00:02:03.920
If you really have evidence,

00:02:04.439 --> 00:02:05.599
then charge me.

00:02:05.920 --> 00:02:07.959
Your room was indeed cleaned thoroughly.

00:02:08.639 --> 00:02:10.000
But in your room,

00:02:10.240 --> 00:02:11.280
we found this.

00:02:14.520 --> 00:02:15.520
Every morning,

00:02:15.759 --> 00:02:16.759
the housekeeping staff

00:02:16.759 --> 00:02:17.879
clean the rooms on schedule.

00:02:19.560 --> 00:02:20.919
The trash they collect

00:02:21.479 --> 00:02:23.039
is temporarily stored in this room.

00:02:23.560 --> 00:02:25.199
Around four in the afternoon,

00:02:25.199 --> 00:02:26.719
a dedicated garbage truck

00:02:27.400 --> 00:02:28.639
hauls everything away.

00:02:29.159 --> 00:02:30.960
Xu Lingling's room

00:02:31.240 --> 00:02:32.080
was just vacated.

00:02:32.319 --> 00:02:33.960
See if you can find any clues.

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:40.400
These are all bath towels.

00:02:41.360 --> 00:02:41.960
Lao Zhao.

00:02:46.319 --> 00:02:47.520
Nitroglycerin pills.

00:02:50.439 --> 00:02:51.080
Wang Kechen,

00:02:51.759 --> 00:02:53.800
as a patient with severe coronary disease,

00:02:54.520 --> 00:02:56.599
any vigorous activity off his meds

00:02:56.840 --> 00:02:58.560
would trigger an attack and kill him.

00:02:59.159 --> 00:03:00.520
He was like a ticking time bomb.

00:03:01.159 --> 00:03:03.120
Wang Kechen's prints are on this bottle.

00:03:03.719 --> 00:03:05.439
We tested the pills inside.

00:03:05.800 --> 00:03:07.039
They're not heart medication.

00:03:07.919 --> 00:03:08.800
They're vitamins.

00:03:10.439 --> 00:03:11.439
Are you saying

00:03:11.919 --> 00:03:13.240
his medication was switched?

00:03:13.840 --> 00:03:15.400
He carried his meds with him every day.

00:03:15.400 --> 00:03:17.159
Anyone could've swapped them.

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:19.039
I wouldn't know about that.

00:03:26.039 --> 00:03:27.560
A Qiang, who set up the honey trap,

00:03:27.879 --> 00:03:28.919
went into your room

00:03:28.919 --> 00:03:30.080
and planted a hidden camera,

00:03:31.439 --> 00:03:32.479
and captured this footage.

00:03:33.159 --> 00:03:34.400
First, you secretly threw away

00:03:34.879 --> 00:03:37.360
Wang Kechen's emergency nitroglycerin.

00:03:37.759 --> 00:03:39.159
After Wang Kechen's death,

00:03:39.879 --> 00:03:41.280
you threw his daily medication

00:03:41.280 --> 00:03:42.280
that prevented sudden death

00:03:42.439 --> 00:03:43.360
into the trash,

00:03:44.199 --> 00:03:46.479
because you'd swapped them with vitamins.

00:03:46.960 --> 00:03:48.159
Your goal in switching the pills

00:03:48.960 --> 00:03:50.879
was to cause Wang Kechen

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:52.560
to die from a heart attack.

00:03:53.120 --> 00:03:54.599
You used Yu Tianfang

00:03:54.599 --> 00:03:56.039
to establish your alibi,

00:03:56.039 --> 00:03:57.240
making Wang Kechen's death

00:03:57.240 --> 00:03:58.639
look more like an accident.

00:04:00.319 --> 00:04:00.840
Yes.

00:04:02.280 --> 00:04:03.120
I did it.

00:04:03.840 --> 00:04:06.240
He wanted to leave it all to his daughter.

00:04:07.240 --> 00:04:08.080
I hated him.

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:10.479
Mr. Wang,

00:04:10.800 --> 00:04:12.080
I need to confirm with you again

00:04:12.680 --> 00:04:13.719
regarding the changes to the will,

00:04:13.719 --> 00:04:15.919
especially the inheritance section.

00:04:16.120 --> 00:04:16.800
Okay.

00:04:18.439 --> 00:04:19.920
I have never properly

00:04:19.920 --> 00:04:21.199
taken care of my own daughter.

00:04:21.480 --> 00:04:22.519
I've now decided

00:04:22.519 --> 00:04:23.839
to leave all of my assets

00:04:24.399 --> 00:04:25.079
to her.

00:04:25.319 --> 00:04:26.639
As a way to make it up to her.

00:04:26.839 --> 00:04:28.040
And I also hope

00:04:28.040 --> 00:04:29.519
that she can forgive me.

00:04:29.519 --> 00:04:30.959
The new will has been revised.

00:04:31.600 --> 00:04:32.759
You just need to sign it.

00:04:34.560 --> 00:04:35.839
But what about your wife,

00:04:36.079 --> 00:04:37.040
Xu Lingling?

00:04:38.439 --> 00:04:38.959
Who did you say?

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:41.079
Your wife, Xu Lingling.

00:04:44.279 --> 00:04:45.360
In my life,

00:04:45.360 --> 00:04:46.920
she's nothing more than a passerby.

00:04:47.879 --> 00:04:49.120
Although I'm fond of her,

00:04:49.879 --> 00:04:51.399
sooner or later, we'll part ways.

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:53.040
Leaving some things

00:04:54.319 --> 00:04:55.600
to her would be completely meaningless.

00:05:15.839 --> 00:05:17.279
This is where I switched the medicine.

00:05:19.199 --> 00:05:20.360
Your motive for murder,

00:05:21.120 --> 00:05:22.600
was it really inheritance?

00:05:23.759 --> 00:05:25.279
I did it, that's all that matters.

00:05:25.560 --> 00:05:27.000
Does it matter what I was thinking?

00:05:27.360 --> 00:05:28.800
What about your first two husbands?

00:05:30.720 --> 00:05:31.800
I can't remember.

00:05:32.959 --> 00:05:33.920
Can I go back now?

00:05:35.199 --> 00:05:35.720
Take her away.

00:05:42.720 --> 00:05:43.360
Why bother?

00:05:44.079 --> 00:05:45.199
For a man like that?

00:05:45.639 --> 00:05:46.800
Don't judge by appearances.

00:05:47.680 --> 00:05:49.040
It's not that simple.

00:05:52.040 --> 00:05:52.680
Slow down.

00:05:55.480 --> 00:05:56.360
Sir, ma'am.

00:05:57.079 --> 00:05:58.600
Do you know Xu Lingling?

00:06:19.120 --> 00:06:22.079
You two are personally taking me to jail?

00:06:22.480 --> 00:06:23.439
I'm honored.

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:24.600
Xu Lingling.

00:06:25.360 --> 00:06:26.839
Confess everything as soon as possible.

00:06:27.199 --> 00:06:28.319
Aim for leniency.

00:06:28.680 --> 00:06:29.519
I plead guilty.

00:06:29.759 --> 00:06:30.560
Just close the case.

00:06:30.759 --> 00:06:31.560
Isn't that enough?

00:06:33.680 --> 00:06:34.959
I've had enough of living.

00:06:36.959 --> 00:06:37.399
Take her away.

00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:39.439
Lingling.

00:06:39.560 --> 00:06:40.079
Lingling.

00:06:40.800 --> 00:06:41.319
Lingling.

00:06:41.319 --> 00:06:42.319
I'm Lingling's mother.

00:06:42.319 --> 00:06:43.000
I need to say a few words to her.

00:06:43.000 --> 00:06:43.600
You two,

00:06:43.720 --> 00:06:44.800
I've told you before.

00:06:44.800 --> 00:06:46.560
You can't meet the suspect privately.

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:48.000
If you need anything, bring a lawyer.

00:06:48.000 --> 00:06:48.639
Officer.

00:06:49.040 --> 00:06:50.079
My daughter is an honest woman.

00:06:50.199 --> 00:06:51.639
She would never commit murder.

00:06:51.959 --> 00:06:52.879
You must be mistaken.

00:06:53.000 --> 00:06:54.000
Please, let her go.

00:06:54.399 --> 00:06:55.560
If you must arrest someone, arrest me.

00:06:55.839 --> 00:06:56.560
I'm begging you.

00:06:57.040 --> 00:06:57.560
Get up.

00:06:57.959 --> 00:06:58.839
Get up, get up, get up.

00:07:02.800 --> 00:07:03.199
Lingling.

00:07:04.040 --> 00:07:05.240
Dad's begging you for one thing.

00:07:06.480 --> 00:07:08.040
Your brother has uremia.

00:07:08.480 --> 00:07:09.480
He needs a kidney transplant.

00:07:10.600 --> 00:07:11.439
None of us are a match.

00:07:11.600 --> 00:07:12.160
Right now,

00:07:12.439 --> 00:07:13.920
you're his only hope.

00:07:13.920 --> 00:07:15.120
Why didn't you mention this before?

00:07:15.879 --> 00:07:16.360
This matter,

00:07:16.720 --> 00:07:18.439
we had to ask our daughter in person.

00:07:18.920 --> 00:07:19.399
Outsiders,

00:07:19.720 --> 00:07:20.480
we can't trust.

00:07:20.600 --> 00:07:21.040
So,

00:07:24.079 --> 00:07:25.360
you came to me

00:07:26.839 --> 00:07:28.360
because you want my kidney.

00:07:29.199 --> 00:07:30.439
How can you say that?

00:07:30.639 --> 00:07:32.120
We're family.

00:07:32.120 --> 00:07:33.439
He's your only brother.

00:07:33.680 --> 00:07:34.560
If you don't save him,

00:07:35.079 --> 00:07:36.920
he won't survive.

00:07:47.160 --> 00:07:48.319
Let me tell you,

00:07:48.600 --> 00:07:50.160
I'd rather be a murderer

00:07:50.160 --> 00:07:51.240
sentenced to death

00:07:51.639 --> 00:07:53.240
than give you my kidney.

00:07:53.800 --> 00:07:54.839
Get out!

00:07:55.879 --> 00:07:56.600
Lingling.

00:07:56.600 --> 00:07:57.319
Please.

00:07:57.319 --> 00:07:58.639
Mom's begging you.

00:07:59.160 --> 00:08:00.120
Lingling.

00:08:01.319 --> 00:08:02.600
I'll say it one more time.

00:08:02.720 --> 00:08:04.040
We have our protocols.

00:08:04.319 --> 00:08:05.759
You can't meet the suspect privately.

00:08:06.519 --> 00:08:07.480
Have your lawyer come.

00:08:07.759 --> 00:08:08.240
Take her away.

00:08:08.240 --> 00:08:09.079
As long as it saves my son,

00:08:09.319 --> 00:08:10.639
I'd rather die.

00:08:11.480 --> 00:08:12.360
I'd rather die!

00:08:12.800 --> 00:08:13.959
Get out!

00:08:15.879 --> 00:08:17.040
Get out!

00:08:22.199 --> 00:08:22.920
Captain Chu.

00:08:25.360 --> 00:08:26.399
Whatever you want to know,

00:08:27.079 --> 00:08:28.120
I'll tell you everything.

00:08:36.279 --> 00:08:37.679
I'm not afraid of hardship.

00:08:39.000 --> 00:08:40.480
I just hate how unfair it is.

00:08:41.039 --> 00:08:42.960
No matter how hard I worked,

00:08:43.759 --> 00:08:45.000
or how hard I studied,

00:08:46.080 --> 00:08:47.240
they didn't care.

00:08:48.360 --> 00:08:50.120
All they cared about was my brother.

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:52.799
They only loved him.

00:08:54.600 --> 00:08:56.360
To take care of him,

00:08:57.480 --> 00:08:58.840
I was forced to drop out of school.

00:08:59.679 --> 00:09:00.720
Right in the darkest moment

00:09:01.120 --> 00:09:02.320
of my life,

00:09:04.320 --> 00:09:05.480
I met Qian Peng.

00:09:09.559 --> 00:09:10.200
Are you okay?

00:09:11.360 --> 00:09:12.399
The groceries are ruined.

00:09:12.879 --> 00:09:13.759
And the bike's broken too.

00:09:13.759 --> 00:09:15.399
My dad's gonna kill me for sure.

00:09:15.799 --> 00:09:16.759
I'll buy you new groceries.

00:09:17.159 --> 00:09:17.879
And I'll fix your bike.

00:09:17.879 --> 00:09:18.600
Come on.

00:09:19.840 --> 00:09:20.679
I'll take you to the hospital.

00:09:27.639 --> 00:09:28.399
Here, careful.

00:09:29.799 --> 00:09:31.000
He was the first man

00:09:32.080 --> 00:09:33.440
who ever cared about me.

00:09:33.879 --> 00:09:35.360
And the first person I knew

00:09:35.360 --> 00:09:36.600
who owned a private car.

00:09:38.080 --> 00:09:39.679
Back then, I thought

00:09:40.759 --> 00:09:42.039
a guy like him

00:09:42.960 --> 00:09:44.279
must be a rich man.

00:09:45.679 --> 00:09:46.519
My name's Qian Peng.

00:09:47.799 --> 00:09:49.000
Meeting like this is fate.

00:09:49.000 --> 00:09:49.879
Let's be friends.

00:09:57.759 --> 00:09:59.080
I thought Qian Peng

00:09:59.279 --> 00:10:00.600
was the only one who could

00:10:00.600 --> 00:10:02.240
save me from that hellhole.

00:10:03.000 --> 00:10:05.039
So I eloped with him to another city.

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:06.360
Not long after,

00:10:06.600 --> 00:10:08.039
we got officially married.

00:10:12.559 --> 00:10:14.360
I was grateful

00:10:14.360 --> 00:10:16.000
that I'd finally changed my fate.

00:10:16.799 --> 00:10:17.600
But I never imagined

00:10:17.960 --> 00:10:19.720
I had jumped from one abyss

00:10:19.960 --> 00:10:21.639
straight into another.

00:10:22.559 --> 00:10:23.840
What kind of man was Qian Peng?

00:10:27.480 --> 00:10:29.080
If my father

00:10:29.080 --> 00:10:30.240
was a tyrant,

00:10:30.960 --> 00:10:32.720
then Qian Peng was a devil.

00:10:34.039 --> 00:10:35.360
After my dad beat me,

00:10:35.879 --> 00:10:37.919
I could still get up and work.

00:10:38.960 --> 00:10:40.360
After Qian Peng beat me,

00:10:40.759 --> 00:10:42.320
I ended up straight in the hospital.

00:10:42.600 --> 00:10:44.039
In less than three years of marriage,

00:10:44.440 --> 00:10:46.399
he broke my bones seven times,

00:10:46.600 --> 00:10:48.240
caused two miscarriages,

00:10:49.120 --> 00:10:50.840
and left me unable to have children.

00:10:53.480 --> 00:10:54.840
Then why didn't you leave him?

00:10:55.480 --> 00:10:56.679
I wanted to run.

00:10:58.240 --> 00:11:00.200
But where could I go?

00:11:00.960 --> 00:11:02.159
I had no money,

00:11:03.200 --> 00:11:04.159
no education,

00:11:05.200 --> 00:11:06.480
no work experience.

00:11:06.639 --> 00:11:08.399
And I sure couldn't go home.

00:11:12.720 --> 00:11:13.639
Tell us, then.

00:11:14.519 --> 00:11:15.840
How exactly did Qian Peng die?

00:11:22.720 --> 00:11:23.960
I remember

00:11:25.080 --> 00:11:26.360
it was pouring rain that day.

00:11:27.320 --> 00:11:28.360
He insisted on going out.

00:11:28.840 --> 00:11:30.480
The streets were flooded.

00:11:30.919 --> 00:11:32.879
A power line had fallen into the water.

00:11:33.080 --> 00:11:34.399
He was electrocuted.

00:11:35.399 --> 00:11:36.440
An accident like that,

00:11:36.840 --> 00:11:38.120
how could I possibly fake it?

00:11:41.480 --> 00:11:42.279
And then?

00:11:44.519 --> 00:11:45.519
Before he died,

00:11:45.519 --> 00:11:47.559
he bought an accident insurance policy.

00:11:48.039 --> 00:11:49.960
I received a large payout.

00:11:50.799 --> 00:11:51.919
At the time, I thought

00:11:53.120 --> 00:11:56.080
insurance was such a wonderful thing.

00:11:59.159 --> 00:12:00.159
Then why did you

00:12:00.399 --> 00:12:01.840
get married a second time?

00:12:02.120 --> 00:12:03.799
For love, of course.

00:12:04.759 --> 00:12:05.600
A woman

00:12:05.799 --> 00:12:07.320
without love

00:12:07.919 --> 00:12:09.600
is no different from a dried fish.

00:12:11.240 --> 00:12:14.080
My second husband, Wang Ping,

00:12:14.600 --> 00:12:15.600
was very gentle.

00:12:16.759 --> 00:12:18.240
He never once hit me.

00:12:22.320 --> 00:12:23.559
He loved gambling at cards.

00:12:25.320 --> 00:12:27.000
He lost all our savings,

00:12:27.879 --> 00:12:28.759
and behind my back,

00:12:29.039 --> 00:12:30.799
secretly borrowed money to buy insurance.

00:12:31.720 --> 00:12:33.879
That day I had to go out for work,

00:12:34.559 --> 00:12:36.200
so I asked Wang Ping to make porridge.

00:12:37.159 --> 00:12:39.519
I even reminded him to turn off the stove.

00:12:40.679 --> 00:12:42.279
I don't know if he did it on purpose

00:12:42.720 --> 00:12:43.679
or just forgot,

00:12:44.039 --> 00:12:45.519
but he fell asleep with the stove on.

00:12:46.279 --> 00:12:47.039
And then,

00:12:47.360 --> 00:12:49.000
he died of gas poisoning.

00:12:50.200 --> 00:12:51.399
I became a widow again.

00:12:53.200 --> 00:12:53.759
Xiao Xu,

00:12:54.279 --> 00:12:54.960
calm down.

00:12:55.440 --> 00:12:56.240
Let's talk this through.

00:13:03.159 --> 00:13:04.639
When the accident happened,

00:13:05.000 --> 00:13:06.480
you just happened to be out?

00:13:08.080 --> 00:13:09.000
That's a bit too convenient, isn't it?

00:13:11.159 --> 00:13:12.600
He cooked the porridge himself.

00:13:13.080 --> 00:13:13.799
If you don't believe me,

00:13:13.799 --> 00:13:15.360
you can check the surveillance footage.

00:13:15.759 --> 00:13:18.039
Why would heaven treat me this way?

00:13:18.879 --> 00:13:19.600
It's been so painful.

00:13:20.639 --> 00:13:22.240
I wanted to die with him.

00:13:22.639 --> 00:13:24.039
Your second husband

00:13:24.039 --> 00:13:25.279
also died in an accident.

00:13:25.279 --> 00:13:26.480
How do you explain that?

00:13:26.480 --> 00:13:28.000
I want to know why too!

00:13:28.519 --> 00:13:29.840
Can you tell me?

00:13:32.559 --> 00:13:33.399
Okay, okay, okay.

00:13:33.840 --> 00:13:34.559
I believe you.